						</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="feature-card text-center group">
						<div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-600 to-teal-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
							<span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">3</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Development & Testing</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
							Your project is built with clean, efficient code and thorough testing is conducted to ensure quality and functionality.
						</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="feature-card text-center group">
						<div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-cyan-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
							<span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">4</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Launch & Optimization</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
							We deploy your project and continuously optimize it for performance, user experience, and business results.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Investment Section -->
		<section class="py-20 bg-white">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
				<div class="text-center mb-16">
					<h2 class="section-title text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
						Your Investment in Digital Growth
					</h2>
					<p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
						A professional website is not an expense—it's an investment in your business's future. Your website works 24/7 to attract customers, build credibility, and drive revenue long after the initial development.
					</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
					<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
						<div class="text-center mb-8">
							<h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
								Starting at $1,000 Initial Investment
							</h3>
							<p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
								Most projects begin with a $1,000 initial investment, which covers project planning, design consultation, and the foundation of your custom website. This investment ensures we start your project with a clear roadmap and a solid foundation tailored to your business goals.
							</p>
							<p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
