							</p>
							<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
								<h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">What Your Investment Delivers:</h4>
								<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-left">
									<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
